title: Large 33 L Backpack
description: The fashion conscious and on-trend American Tourister patron prefers to step-out in style no matter the occasion. Be it a trip to the gym, for regular use or a vacation we have a design to suit every need. Like all products from the brand, our backpacks meet the highest quality standards for which American Tourister is known. This attention to detail is reflected in the positive feedback from our customers in 100+ countries. Show off your sporty side with this voluminous backpack that comes with multiple compartments & a separate rain cover compartment which make it perfect for your college/office or outdoor travel. This backpack made of premium twill polyester fabric, is equipped with 3 full compartments to hold enough notebooks, textbooks & journals for your college or clothes & other essentials for a weekend trip. Tractum Suspension Straps with shock absorption helps reduce load on shoulders making your 5-kg backpack seem a lot lighter. The backpack has an internal organizer that provides easy access to your phone charger, stationery or whatever you need on the go and still has ample space left for your headphones, your personal diary or the novel you’re reading on your commute. It has padded mesh back & shoulder straps with breathable system for better back support. It comes with pockets on both sides to comfortably accommodate your bottle or umbrella for convenience of access. Protect your bag from rainy weather or dust with a lightweight, packable rain cover that’s made with an adjustable elastic closure for a secure fit around your backpack.
